  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GET READY FOR THE FIGHT, TIME IS TICKING!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075720/extras/0e5c0ce26e2ca0c51ccc72a99d20641d.poster.avif?t=1768469864\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075720/extras/0e5c0ce26e2ca0c51ccc72a99d20641d.webm?t=1768469864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075720/extras/0e5c0ce26e2ca0c51ccc72a99d20641d.mp4?t=1768469864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have 9 Days to explore the vast world to find the best skills and items for the final fight. Choose carefully where you go and how you spend your time. Remember, you only have 9 days!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CRAFT YOUR FIGHTNING STYLE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075720/extras/2964d7b8c7bfef0197c6e51bc84d69a7.poster.avif?t=1768469864\" width=800 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075720/extras/2964d7b8c7bfef0197c6e51bc84d69a7.webm?t=1768469864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075720/extras/2964d7b8c7bfef0197c6e51bc84d69a7.mp4?t=1768469864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft your own style of fighting by mixing different Ki Attacks, Dodges and Melee Strikes together. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>YOU HAVE 9 DAYS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During the 9th day, the time for exploration is over. You will be confronted by Afran to determine the fate of the world.</p>",
